---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Your Name — Interests" activeNav="/interests">
    <h1 class="mb-4">Interests</h1>
    <p class="text-gray-400 mb-10 max-w-2xl">
        Beyond academics, here's what I'm passionate about and what keeps me curious.
    </p>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-14">
        <!-- Interest 1 -->
        <div class="card group">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-primary/20 flex items-center justify-center text-primary-light flex-shrink-0">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M3 9a2 2 0 012-2h.93a2 2 0 001.664-.89l.812-1.22A2 2 0 0110.07 4h3.86a2 2 0 011.664.89l.812 1.22A2 2 0 0018.07 7H19a2 2 0 012 2v9a2 2 0 01-2 2H5a2 2 0 01-2-2V9z" />
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M15 13a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z" />
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <h3 class="text-lg mb-2">Photography</h3>
                    <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
                        <!-- Update with your photography interests -->
                        I love capturing moments and telling stories through the lens. Whether it's
                        street photography, landscapes, or portraits, photography helps me see the
                        world from different perspectives. Check out my work on the
                        <a href="/photography">Photography</a> page.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Interest 2 -->
        <div class="card group">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-accent/20 flex items-center justify-center text-accent flex-shrink-0">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13 7h8m0 0v8m0-8l-8 8-4-4-6 6" />
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <h3 class="text-lg mb-2">Economics & Markets</h3>
                    <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
                        <!-- Update with your specific economic interests -->
                        Fascinated by how markets work, behavioral economics, and the intersection
                        of data and economic policy. I enjoy following macroeconomic trends and
                        understanding how data-driven insights shape decision-making.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Interest 3 -->
        <div class="card group">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-primary/20 flex items-center justify-center text-primary-light flex-shrink-0">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M3.055 11H5a2 2 0 012 2v1a2 2 0 002 2 2 2 0 012 2v2.945M8 3.935V5.5A2.5 2.5 0 0010.5 8h.5a2 2 0 012 2 2 2 0 104 0 2 2 0 012-2h1.064M15 20.488V18a2 2 0 012-2h3.064M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <h3 class="text-lg mb-2">Travel & Culture</h3>
                    <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
                        <!-- Update with your travel/culture interests -->
                        Exploring new places and cultures broadens my perspective. I enjoy immersing
                        myself in different environments, trying local food, and capturing it all
                        through my camera.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Interest 4 -->
        <div class="card group">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-accent/20 flex items-center justify-center text-accent flex-shrink-0">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9.663 17h4.673M12 3v1m6.364 1.636l-.707.707M21 12h-1M4 12H3m3.343-5.657l-.707-.707m2.828 9.9a5 5 0 117.072 0l-.548.547A3.374 3.374 0 0014 18.469V19a2 2 0 11-4 0v-.531c0-.895-.356-1.754-.988-2.386l-.548-.547z" />
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <h3 class="text-lg mb-2">Data & Storytelling</h3>
                    <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
                        <!-- Update with your interests -->
                        I believe data tells a story. I'm interested in how visualization and
                        analysis can make complex information accessible and drive meaningful
                        insights for organizations and communities.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- What I'm Currently Into -->
    <section class="mb-14">
        <h2 class="section-heading">What I'm Currently Reading / Following</h2>
        <div class="card">
            <div class="space-y-4">
                <!-- Update these with your actual current interests -->
                <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                    <span class="text-primary-light mt-1">&#8226;</span>
                    <p class="text-gray-300 text-sm">
                        <span class="font-medium">Book/Podcast Title</span>
                        <span class="text-gray-400"> — Brief description of why it interests you.</span>
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                    <span class="text-primary-light mt-1">&#8226;</span>
                    <p class="text-gray-300 text-sm">
                        <span class="font-medium">Newsletter / Blog</span>
                        <span class="text-gray-400"> — What you enjoy about it and what you've learned.</span>
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                    <span class="text-primary-light mt-1">&#8226;</span>
                    <p class="text-gray-300 text-sm">
                        <span class="font-medium">Topic You're Exploring</span>
                        <span class="text-gray-400"> — A new area of curiosity you're diving into.</span>
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</Layout>
